TLDW: I took the tier lists from Tempo Storm, Vicious Syndicate, hearthstone-decks.net, and Rankstar and calculated tier scores for each deck archetype while removing archetypes that were only mentioned in 1 or 2 reports. I then averaged out the scores to produce an aggregated Wild Meta Snapshot. Here is the tier list:
